Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Out.\N- Birdman
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No response, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no pedals. It looks like a glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter. Let us make it our\Njurisdiction regardless of its lack of wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My shadowy business role is as the Master\NSergeant of the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sell off illegally parked bicycles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and am using that as the basis for forming\Nmy gorgeous rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delicious sake, food, women flocking to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The business may have\Na bit of a bad reputation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the way of the world is the\Ngreater the villainy, the greater the glory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have my pick of raven-haired maidens...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I have money,\NI can have anything I want!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant, a woman\Nfrom Birdman is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, some woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to Lake Biwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the plane that we all made together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be sold for a high price to a\Ncertain important person in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make an even better plane,\Nwe could sell it for even more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about I become your sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what of it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This world is all a power game, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no such thing as pure love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love is nothing but a fleeting illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Realize the truth about society, everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing in this world\Nthat cannot be bought with money!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what is this pain I feel in my heart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:54.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before me lay open innumerable\Ndoors to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had already come to my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the many fliers,\Nonly one was conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sink or swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Society Lucky\NCat Chinese Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can learn the other\Nsides of a lot of different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a fun experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what does "Secret Society" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, we have a prospective new hire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Aijima, the manager of the Lucky\NCat Chinese Restaurant. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please read this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't actually expect an organization\Nthat wrote "Secret Society" on their flier{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to actually be a secret society,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant\Nis one, exactly as the sign said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their branches include the\NLibrary Police, the Print Shop,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps,\Nand a bunch of other unofficial circles...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taken all together, they are\Nthe Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, they have a hand in all\Nthe underhanded business at the school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and are the organization that\Nessentially controls the university.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, once you've read the menu you\Nwill not be allowed to quit our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do quit the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a little process called "paying the bill"\Nwill be waiting to erase you from society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gather every single piece of\Npersonal information about the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which videos you rented\Nfrom the video rental store,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what you bought from the\Nsupermarket or convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which books you read,\Nwhich transmissions you sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even what you smelled\Nlike when you were a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no intention of turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show them all by climbing to the\Ntop of this Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good look you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now I will assign you to the Library Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to have you on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There stood an ominous man\Nwith an evil face of ill portent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that man has made a giant\Nplaything out of my fate ever since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The original aim of the Library Police{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was to chase down the scoundrels who\Nhad not returned materials to the library{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to recover the lent books by force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the goal eventually\Ndeviated from how it had started,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and most peoples' secrets\Nand personal information{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were accumulated by the Library Police--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}people both inside and outside of Kyoto,\Nfrom Oohara's Sanzen Temple in the north{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to Uji's Byoudou\NTemple's Houou Hall in the south.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's now even an organization\Nthat helps participate in politics.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed, those who control\Ninformation, control the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will rise in rank, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and get to a place where\NI can handle all the information I want!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I quickly ran into a strange\Nindividual whom I was to collect from.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi Seitarou, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That copy of Jules Verne's {\i1}20,000 Leagues\NUnder the Sea {\i0}is more than a year overdue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your duty as a library patron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi-{\i1}san{\i0}, it's way\Npast the due date, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is... But just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been four\Nmonths since you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta hit the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, unable to collect a\Nsingle book for more than a year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won fame as the greatest failure\Nin the history of the Library Police.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the other hand,\NOzu used all kinds of techniques{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to recover books from the evil\Noverduers and was promoted for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, he spun an\Nunfathomable web of human connections,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and rose even in his first year to\Nbecome the right hand man to Aijima-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why does a human\Nlike you end up being promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unimpeachable character,\Nconversational skills, clear thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a cute appearance, and copious amounts\Nof overflowing love for your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the secrets to being loved by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll kill you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live some meaningless\Nlife enjoying the unhappiness of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, no matter how hard you work,\NI'll do my best to make sure you turn out no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:28.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Philippine Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are tied together by a dark thread, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't until far later\Nthat I came to understand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Mr. Higuchi's impromptu\Nescapes were aided by Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in my way, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. He's my Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please overlook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand New
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that'll cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,June of my second year, finally\Nrealizing I had no talent at collecting books,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "restaurant" transferred\Nme to the Print Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Print Shop is an organization\Nin control of many excellent students
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which mass produces fraudulent reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always at hand to save students facing a crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my job was to deliver the\Nfinished reports to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get promoted faster,\NI took on a large number of customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,delivering the reports using a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that incident,\Nover 200 students failed credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the worst disaster in the history of\Nthe Print Shop, and it lost the customers' faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was an acquaintance of Ozu,\Nhe couldn't be so obvious about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Aijima-{\i1}senpai {\i0}had been putting\Nmore and more distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then spoke to me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a side job. Help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s front
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the President of the library and\Nsupervisor of the Movie Circle Misogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the jester in Mr. Jougasaki's court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission was to collect information on\Na new recruit and allow him to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you do on the weekends, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you\Nsomething like that, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-M-M-Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called Mochiguman\Nand they come in sets of five...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? One's missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\NI think something flew off when you fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, it's dangerous. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but it's always come\Nback to me, even if I didn't search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, having broken Aijima-senpai's mood,\Nwas demoted to the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps is a group\Nthat manages the illegal parking of bicycles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is a major source of funds for\Nthe Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weak-kneed wimp! Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This organization does not suit my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of revealing\NAijima and all the crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant has\Ncommitted through the years and escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous. You'll end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Squish
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I'm using brilliant\Nmaneuvers to cover for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try being a little grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grateful? Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-{\i1}senpai {\i0}is definitely trouble, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interested in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really... Though, where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched it out using the\Ninformation network of the Library Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Akashi-{\i1}san {\i0}said she lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed clues, but it was quite the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like it was wandering around\Ntrying to be picked up by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very busy playing the game of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, I can't just... So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dutch wife we're targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki has named it Kaori,\Nand we're going to take it from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to earn the respect of Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-{\i1}senpai {\i0}decided to\Nplay a prank on Mr. Jougasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people know of the depressing things\Ncalled "Dutch Wives" in this world. Even I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this elegant\Nexpression Kaori-{\i1}san {\i0}has?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a face that speaks\Nout to the corrupt morals of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carefully combed hair,\Nthe exquisitely prepared dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed the depth of Mr. Jougasaki's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I, as a human being, allow the delicate and\Nsubtle world these two created to be destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is the height of heresy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping Kaori-{\i1}san {\i0}and using her\Nto threaten Mr. Jougasaki I will not allow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let this happen!\NIt is a very refined, pure love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand loving\Nsome doll that's not alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even puts lipstick on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stepping on other people's pure love for\Nthe sake of your own desire is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting your private\Ndesires influence your public missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to lay a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course I did not say that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I instead chose a strategic withdrawal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be a\Npart of something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had finally gone and done it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will surely be erased from\Nsociety by Aijima's power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, opportunity is always dangling\Nin front of your eyes. Please grab onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 9,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost 5 figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ran and hid in a manga café on\NKitashira River, shaking like newborn fawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But no one came after me, and a week\Nafterwards Aijima-senpai lost his standing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,New Hero -- Bra-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima Bra-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the Filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Animal Abuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:43.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lipstick Licker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for the ladies' locker room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Spits in your tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy Fetishist! Panty Sniffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become the Manager of\Nthe Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, don't give me a bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-{\i1}senpai {\i0}was running the\Norganization for his personal use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I spoke with the executive board\Nof the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was vaguely apprehensive. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What else could I be but\Na Renaissance man of fear?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time you\Ntake this lucky chance to enjoy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu Establishes his Government
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I assumed the office of the Master\NSergeant of the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At first I was somewhat\Nskeptical of this activity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I became more and more absorbed in it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}directing it with a passion to take back\Nthe two previous years that had gone wasted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The organization acted exactly as\NI desired. It felt quite good, actually.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This might be that rose-colored\Ncampus life I wished for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cornucopia of raven-haired\Nmaidens to choose from!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be my ideal? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was no easy task getting here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I had finally obtained it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was all too easy to grasp once I tried!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:14:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had once been led astray\Nby an adherence to pure love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I finally realized. Everything\Nin this world revolved around money!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant, I have\Nsomething excellent to tell you of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be quite profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in the Birdman Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that was the result, as you clearly saw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have had everything I wanted.\NDid I make a mistake somewhere, somehow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! I have finished! I'm finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This. This morning I finished\Nmy journey of more than two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so moved I wanted to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was some good times, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am hungry. Would you\Nlike to go eat some ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I left the university a few days ago\N I ran into an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were not looking so comfortable\Nat all, and hurried off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're in the same year as you,\NMaster, they're probably a doctoral student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder they felt awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they be embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not them who had to repeat classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is the very reason\Nyou are the Master, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about this for quite a\Nwhile, but now my mind is made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be the day for me\Nto go forth, out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will circle the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like something went awry with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life has not yet begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are spending overtime\Ninside of your mother's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I successfully obtained a life\Nthat people would be jealous of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some\Nmore meaningful life out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More rose-colored, more sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might have been some
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,college life with not a single dark\Ncloud that would have satisfied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Are you half asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to where I am by\Nbelieving in my own potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I'm saying it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why does my heart feel so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's a choice I should have made\Nthat would have led to some other possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the choices I made\Nin my first year were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot use the word\N"possibility" without limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a bunny girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a famous singer, or a\Nsuperhero who saves the world with his powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you keep focusing your gaze on\Nthat which is unrealistic, you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The root of all your evil
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in always relying on one of your\Nother possibilities to get your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must accept that you\Nare the person here, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you cannot become\Nanyone else other than that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that you can lead some\Nworthwhile college life and feel satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it, so have confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no such thing as\Nthat rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? Because there is\Nnothing rose-colored in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is all a bunch\Nof colors mixed up, you see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what perfect timing, meeting you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ponto Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you were pretty cool\Nuntil you ran away from Aijima-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fooled by Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met him, I wouldn't have\Ncompletely wasted these two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's selfish and arrogant, lazy and perverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He eats people's unhappiness with\Nthree helpings of rice, and that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his feelings are pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}feels about his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never believe that\NOzu would have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he met her as a\Nfreshman in the tennis circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went with her to see the Gozan festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were tossed around in the\Ncrowd of people and she ended up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year he plans to see\Nall five mountains at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any place you\Ncan see all five at once from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not unless you're in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu used the members of the Lucky Cat\NChinese Restaurant for his own personal uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mixed up his private and public duties too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's snuck into the\NHonwaka Group's headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is planning on stealing the airship there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal Distribution of Funds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To Honwaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he hid his tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I know he has a woman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Steal Airship
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the daughter of the head of Honwaka Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning on using that airship for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honwaka's Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was indeed a bolt out of the blue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I had misjudged Ozu all this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ozu has a girlfriend? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was his rise to the top\Nall for such a pure reason?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His goal wasn't simply to\Nspend his time meaninglessly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He plans to take off from here and pick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the girl in the facility on the next mountain over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, especially, I won't let get your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite the persistent one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu had a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crashed! Surround the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I had done had all been meaningless,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I had thought that it was the same for Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, Ozu had enjoyed his\Nmeaningless campus life to his heart's content,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he had a girlfriend,\Nand was even a fool in love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I the only one who wasted his life?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Immediately after I was born,\NI was the incarnation of innocence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Loved as much as baby\NHikaru Genji was by Kaguya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With not a hint of a wicked thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was said my smile would illuminate\Nthe countryside around my hometown{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the light of love. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what of me now? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this how you plan to settle\Nyour accounts, as you are?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is the one responsible? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it will always turn out like this,\Nthen I should do nothing at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be best not to set foot\Noutside of the 4.5 tatami room!{\i0}
